                    <img
                       src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Group_522.png?v=1657477294"
                       loading="lazy"
                     />
                  </div>
                  <div class="item">
                    <div class="title">No more keys to carry</div>
                    <div class="des">Fingerprint unlock provide maximum convenience whenever you hop on the e-bike. No more hassle worrying about losing another key.</div>
